properties.name: NIH Toolbox Hearing Threshold Test
properties.definition_text: This automated audiometric test measures hearing thresholds at six different frequencies, separately in the left and right ears. The frequencies presented are: .5, 1, 2, 4, 6 and 8 kHz.
